hadiths[126]{hadithnumber,text}:
3661,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney meri itaat ki usney Allah ki itaat ki, jisney meri nafarmani ki usney Allah ki nafarmani ki, jisney ameer ki itaat ki usney meri itaat ki, aur jisney ameer ki nafarmani ki usney meri nafarmani ki, aur Imam dhaal hai uskey zer saya qitaal kya jata hai aur uskey zariey bacha jata hai, agar usney Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karney ka hukm diya aur adl kya to us wajeh se uskey liye ajr hai, aur agar usney uskey ilawa kuch kaha to uska gunah is par hoga .'' muttafaq aleh."
3662,"Hazrat Umme-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar kisi naak aur kaan katey ghulam ko tumhara ameer muqarrar kar diya jaey aur wo Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq tumhari raahnumai karey to phir uski baat suno aur itaat karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3663,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar kisi Habshi ghulam ko, jis ka sar angoor ki tarah chhota sa ho, tum par aamil ( governer ( muqarrar kar diya jaey to uski baat suno aur itaat karo.'' Bukhari ."
3664,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman shakhs par her pasand w napasand mein samaa w itaat lazim hai b-sharte-ke usey gunah ka hukm na diya jaey, jab usey gunah ka hukm diya jaey to phir na sunna hai aur na itaat karna hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3665,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' gunah mein koi itaat nahin, itaat to sirf maroof ( sharae umur (baton) ( mein hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3666,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne tangi w aasani , khushgawari w nagawari , apney nazar andaz kiye janey aur dusron ko tarjeeh diye janey par , ameer ko maazul na karney par, her jagah haq baat karney par aur Allah ( ki razamandi ke mamley ( mein , malamat gar ki malamat se na darney par , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki samaa w itaat ikhtiyar karney par baiat ki. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : jab tak ham daleel ke mutabiq ameer mein Allah ka sareeh kufr na dekhen us se dast itaat na kheenchein .'' muttafaq aleh."
3667,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ham samaa w itaat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat kartey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen farmatey : '' us ( mamley ( mein jiski tum istataat rakho .'' muttafaq aleh."
3668,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney ameer mein koi naa-pasandida chiz dekhey to wo sabr karey, kyonkey jo shakhs baalisht barabar jamaat se alehdgi ikhtiyar karkey faut ho jaey to wo jahiliyat ki si maut marta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3669,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs itaat chhod kar , jamaat se alag ho kar , faut ho jaey to wo jahiliyat ki si maut martaa hai. jo shakhs andhey parcham taley qitaal (jang) karta hai, asbiyat (dushmani) ki wajeh se naraz hota hai ya asbiyat ki dawat deta hai, ya asbiyat ki madad karta hai, aur wo us haalat mein qatl kar diya jaey to wo jahiliyat par qatl hota hai. jo shakhs meri ummat ke khilaf talwaar soont kar nikal aata hai aur wo is (ummat) ke nek aur faajir (badkar) ko maarta hai aur wo na to kisi momin ki parwah karta hai aur na kisi muaahida ki to wo mujh se nahin aur main us se nahin hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
3670,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey behtareen Imam wo hain jinhen tum pasand kartey ho aur wo tumhen pasand kartey hain, tum unke haq mein duayen kartey ho aur wo tumharey haq mein duayen kartey hain, aur tumharey bad-tareen Imam wo hain jin ko tum napasand kartey ho aur wo tumhen napasand kartey hain, tum un par lanat bhejtey ho aur wo tum par lanat bhejtey hain.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, ham ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya us waqt ham unhen unke oahadon se na hata den? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin ! jab tak wo tum mein Namaz qaaim karen, nahin ! jab tak wo tum mein Namaz ka ehtimam karaein , sun lo ! jis par koi haakim aur sarparast muqarrar kiya jaey aur wo Allah ki kisi gunah ka amal karey to usey chahiye ke wo Allah ki nafarmani ko napasand karey aur wo itaat se munh na fere.'' rawahu Muslim."
3671,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum par aisey hukmran hongey ke tum unke baaz kaamon ko achchha janogey aur baaz ko buraa, jisney inkar kiya to wo mudahinat aur nifaq se bari ho gaya aur jisney naa-pasandeedgi ka izhar kiya to wo (wabal sey) bach gaya, lekin jo razi ho gaya aur unke peechhey laga (to wo nifaq wabal mein shareek ho gaya).'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : kya ham un se qitaal na keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, jab tak wo Namaz padhein, nahin, jab tak wo Namaz padhein.'' yani jisney apney dil se napasand kiya aur apney dil se inkar kiya. rawahu Muslim."
3672,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein farmaya : ''tum an-qareeb merey baad tarjeeh deney ko aur aisey umur (baton) ko dekhogey jinhen tum napasand kartey hongey.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap hamen kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unka haq unhen do aur apna haq Allah se talab karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
3673,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Salma bin Yazid Jaafi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to arz kiya : Allah ke Nabi ! mujhey bataeyn agar ham par aisey Ameer muqarrar ho jaeyn jo apna haq ham se talab karen jabkey hamarey haq se hamein mehroom rakhen tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''suno aur itaat karo, jo unki zimmedaari hai wo uskey mukallaf hain, aur jo tumhari zimmedaari hai tum uskey zimmedar aur mukallaf ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
3674,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne (ameer ki) itaat se haath khinch liya to wo roze-qiyamat Allah se us haal mein mulaqat kerega ke uskey paas koi hujjat aur uzr nahin hoga, aur jo shakhs us haal mein faut hua ke uski gardan mein ameer ki baiat nahin to wo jahiliyat ki si maut mara.'' rawahu Muslim."
3675,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Bani-Israel ke umur (baton) ki sarparasti aur islah Anbiya (Alaihissalam) kiya kartey they, jab koi Nabi faut ho jata to uskey baad eik aur Nabi aa jata jabke merey baad koi Nabi nahin, aur albatta an-qareeb bahut se khulafaa hongey.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : aap hamein kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum (tarteeb waar) pehley aur phir uskey baad waley ki baiat puri karo, tum unka haq ada karo, kyonkey Allah un se us chiz ke barey mein sawal karney wala hai jo usney unhen nigehbani aur hukmrani ata ki hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3676,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab do khaleefaon ke liye baiat ki jaey to un mein se doosrey ko qatl kar do.'' rawahu Muslim."
3677,"Hazrat Arfaja (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''an-qareeb mukhtalif qism ke fasaadaat hongey, jo shakhs ummat ke ittihaad ko paara paara karney ki koshish karey to usey talwaar ke sath qatl kar do chahey (chaahe) wo koi ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
3678,"Hazrat Arfaja (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jo shakhs tumharey paas aaye , jabkey tumhara maamla eik shakhs par jama ho, aur wo shakhs tumhari quwat ko bikherna ya tumhari jama'iyat ko muntashir karna chahta ho to usey qatl kar do.'' rawahu Muslim."
3679,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi Imam ki baiat kar ley , uski itaat ikhtiyar kar ley aur wo ikhlas ke sath uskey sath lag jaey to phir wo taqat bhar uski itaat karey, aur phir agar koi aur aa kar us (Imam awwal ya baiat karney waley) ko hataney ki koshish karey to phir doosrey ki gardan udado.'' rawahu Muslim."
3680,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''amaarat talab na karna , kyonkey agar tumhari khahish par wo tumhen de-di gaee to tum uskey supurd kar diye jaaogey , aur agar wo tumhari talab aur khahish ke baghair tumhen ata ki gaee to phir is par tumhari madad ki jaeygi.'' muttafaq aleh."
3681,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb tum amaarat milney ki hirs aur koshish karogey, aur roze-qiyamat wo (tumharey liye) baaise nadaamat hogi, uska milna achchha hai aur uska chhin jana bura hai.'' Bukhari."
3682,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey aamil (governer) kyon nahin muqarrar farma detey? wo bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey kandhey par haath maar kar farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! tum kamzor aadmi ho, jabkey wo eik amanat hai, jis shakhs ne usey uskey haq ke mutabiq na liya aur na uski zimme-daariyon ko nibhaayaa to wo roze-qiyamat us shakhs ke liye baaise ruswai aur nadaamat hogi .'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''Abu-Zar ! main tumhen kamzor samajhta hun, main jo apney liye pasand karta hun wohi tumharey liye pasand karta hun, tum kabhi do aadmiyon par bhi ameer na banna aur na kisi yateem ke maal ki sarparasti qubul karna.'' rawahu Muslim."
3683,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur merey do chacha-zaad , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to un mein se eik ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ne jin umur (baton) par aap ko sarparast banaya hai un mein se baaz par hamen ameer muqarrar farma den, aur doosrey shakhs ne bhi isi tarah kaha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! be-shak ham us kaam par kisi aisey shakhs ko ameer nahin banatey jo uska mutalba karey aur na hi uski hirs rakhney waley shakhs ko hukmran banatey hain.'' dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham apney amal par kisi aisey shakhs ko aamil muqarrar nahin kartey jo uski khahish karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3684,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum logon mein se us shakhs ko behtareen paaogey jo us Amr (hukoomat aur amaarat) ko intehai napasand karta hai yahan tak ke wo is mein mubtala na ho jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3685,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! tum sab nigehban ho aur tum sab apni zimmedari ke mutalliq jawab deh ho, hukmran jo logon ka nigehban hai wo apni zimmedari ke mutalliq jawab deh hai, aadmi apney ehle khana ka nigehban hai aur wo apni zimmedari ke mutalliq jawab deh hai, aurat apney khawind ke ghar aur uski aulad ki zimmedar hai aur wo unke mutalliq jawab deh hai aur aadmi ka ghulam apney aaqa ke maal ka nigehban hai aur wo uskey mutalliq jawab deh hai. sun lo ! tum sab nigehban ho aur tum sab apni zimmedari ke mutalliq jawab deh ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
3686,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo hukmran musalmanon ke kisi maamlat ka zimmedar baney aur wo un se mukhlis na ho aur usey usi haalat mein maut aa jaey to Allah ne is par jannat ko haram qarar dey diya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3687,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah jis bandey ko kisi zimmedari ka nigehban banaey aur wo unke sath khair-khahi na karey to wo jannat ki khushbu bhi nahin paeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
3688,"Hazrat Aaid bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''bad-tareen nigehban , zalim shakhs hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3689,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! jo shakhs meri ummat ka hukmran baney aur wo un par sakhti karey to to bhi is par sakhti kar , aur jis shakhs ko meri ummat ka hukmran banaya jaey aur wo un par narmi karey to to bhi is par narmi kar.'' rawahu Muslim."
3690,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insaf karney waley Allah ke yahan Rehman ke daain taraf Noor ke membaron par hongey aur uskey dono haath daain hain, aur wo log apney hukm mein , apney ehale khana se aur apni zimmedari ke maamlat mein insaf kartey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
3691,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne jis Nabi ko bhi Nabi banakar bheja aur jis kisi ko khalifa muqarrar farmaya to uskey do khususi musheer hotey hain, eik musheer usey neki ka hukm deta hai usey is par aamada karta hai jabkey eik musheer usey buraai ka hukm deta hai aur usey is par aamada karta hai aur bachta wohi hai jisey Allah bachaey.'' Bukhari."
3692,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ka Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan wo maqam tha jo hukmran ke yahan kotwaal ka hota hai. Bukhari."
3693,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye khabar pahunchi ke ehale Faaris ne Kisraa ki beti ko apna hukmran bana liya hai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo qom kabhi falah nahin paeygi jisney apney umur (baton) kisi aurat ke supurd kar diye.'' Bukhari.
3694,"Hazrat Haris Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen paanch chizon : jamaat se wabasta rehney , samaa aur itaat (Listen and obey), hijrat aur Allah ki raah mein jihad karney ka hukm deta hun. aur jis shakhs ne baalisht bhar jamaat se alehdgi ikhtiyar ki to usney Islam ki rassi apni gardan se utaar di, magar ye ke wo lot aaye , aur jis shakhs ne jahiliyat ka na'ra buland kiya uska shumar jahannamiyon mein se hoga. agar-che wo roza rakhey aur Namaz padhey aur wo guman karey ke wo musalman hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
3695,"Hazrat Ziyad bin Kaseeb Adwi bayan kartey hain, main Abu-Bakra ke sath ibne Aamir ke member ke paas tha jabkey ibne Aamir khutba dey raha tha aur usney bareek libas pehna hua tha, (ye dekh kar) Abu Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamarey ameer ko dekho usney faasiqon jaisa libas pehan rakha hai, Abu-Bakra ne kaha : khamosh ho jaao. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne Allah ke sultan ki zamin mein ihaanat ki to Allah uski ihaanat kerega.'' Tirmizi. aur unhoney kaha ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3696,"Hazrat Nawaas bin Samaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khaliq ki nafarmani mein makhluq ki koi itaat nahin.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3697,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''das afrad ke ameer ko bhi us haal mein laya jaeyga ke uska haath gardan ke sath bandhaa hoga yahan tak ke (us ka ( adl usey azad kara dega, ya (us ka ( zulm usey halak kara dega.'' rawahu Darmi."
3698,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ameeron ke liye wail (halakat aur tabahi ya jahannam ki eik wadi) hai. naazemeen ke liye halakat hai aur amanat rakhney walon ke liye halakat hai, roze-qiyamat log aarzu karengey ke unki peshaaniyaan surayyaa ke sath muallaq (adhar mein latki hui) hotin wo zamin aur aasman ke darmiyan harkat kartey rehtey lekin wo kisi kaam ki zimme-daari aur sarparasti qubul na kartey.'' aur Imam Ahmed ne bhi isey riwayat kiya hai, unki riwayat mein hai ke unke baal surayyaa ke sath muallaq hotey aur wo zamin aur aasman ke darmiyan harkat kartey rehtey lekin unhen kisi kaam ki zimme-daari na sonpi jati.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah aur Ahmed)."
3699,"Hazrat Ghalib Qataan eik aadmi se aur wo apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Nazim ka hona zaroori hai kyonkey naazimon ke baghair guzaara mumkin nahin, lekin (aksar) Nazim jahannam mein hongey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3700,"Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''main nadanon ki amaarat se tumhen Allah ki panah mein deta hun.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo kya chiz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey baad kuchh Ameer hongey, jo shakhs unke paas jaey unki jhoot bayaani par unki tasdeeq karey aur unke zulm par unki madad karey to aisey log mujh se nahin hain aur main un se nahin hun aur wo hoze kausar par merey paas nahin aaeyngey , aur jo shakhs unke paas jaey na unki jhoot bayaani par unki tasdeeq karey aur na hi unke zulm par unki madad karey to aisey log mujh se hain aur main un se hun aur yehi log hoz par merey paas aaeyngey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
3701,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jangal mein rehney wala sakht dil hota hai. shikar ka peechha karney wala ghafil hota hai aur badshah ke paas janey wala fitney ka shikar ho jata hai.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs badshah ke sath laga rehta hai to wo fitney ka shikar ho jata hai, jis qadr koi shakhs badshah ke qarib hota hai wo usi qadr Allah se door ho jata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Ahmed, Nasai aur Abu-Dawood."
3702,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadi Karb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (az-raahe-mohabbat) uskey kandhon par haath maara, phir farmaya : ''Qudaim! agar tum ameer, munshi aur naazim baney baghair faut huey to tum kamiyab huey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3703,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tax wasul karney wala (yani wo shakhs jo logon se khilafe-shareh tax wasul karta hai) jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
3704,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat ke din Allah ke nazdik tamam logon mein mehbub tar aur buland martaba, aadil haakim hoga aur us se door, bad-tareen aur martaba mein past w zaleel zalim haakim hoga.'' Tirmizi. aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi."
3705,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sab se fazilat wala jihad us shakhs ka hai jo zalim hukmran ke samney kalma haq kehta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3706,Hazrat Imam Ahmed aur Imam Nasai ne usey Tariq bin Shahab se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed w Nasai.
3707,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah kisi hukmran ke sath bhalai ka irada farmata hai to usey sacha wazir inayat farma deta hai, agar wo bhool jaey to wo ( wazir ( usey yad kara deta hai aur agar usey khud hi yad ho to wo uski madad karta hai, aur jab wo uskey sath uskey bar-aks irada farmata hai to uskey liye bura wazir muqarrar kar deta hai, agar wo bhool jaey to wo ( wazir ( usey yad nahin karata , aur agar usey yad ho to phir wo uski madad nahin karta .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3708,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo hukmran logon ke uyoob talash karta rehta hai to wo unhen kharab kar deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3709,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab tum logon ke uyoob talash karogey to tum unhen kharab kar dogey .'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
3710,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum us waqt kya karogey jab merey baad hukmran is maale-ghanimat ko apney paas hi rakh lengey?'' maine arz kya is zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja! main apni talwaar apney kandhey par rakhunga, phir qitaal karunga yahan tak ke aap se aa miloon. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen us chiz se behtar chiz ke mutalliq na bataaun? sabr karna yahan tak ke tum mujh se aa milo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3711,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho, roze-qiyamat Allah azz-w-jall ke saye ki taraf sabqat ley janey waley kon hongey ?'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo log jinhen kalma haq (pesh kya) jata hai to wo usey qubul kartey hain, jab us se haq baat kehney ka mutalba kya jata hai to usey bayan kartey hain aur wo logon ke liye wohi faisla kartey hain jo wo apni zaat ke liye kartey hain.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3712,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''mujhey apni ummat ke mutalliq teen chizon ka andesha hai : sitaron ke zariey barish talab karney , badshah ka zulm karna aur taqdir ko jhutlana .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3713,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chhe roz mujhey farmatey rahey : ''abu-Zar! jo kuch tujhey bataya ja raha hai usey yad kar lo.'' jab uskey baad saatwan roz hua to farmaya : ''main terey zahiri w batni umur (baton) mein tujhey Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karney ki wasiyat karta hun, aur jab to buraai kar bethey to phir neki kar , aur kisi se koi chiz na maangna chahey tumhara kudra gir padey , aur amanat na rakh aur do aadmiyon ke darmiyan faisla na karna.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3714,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne das ya us se zayed afrad ke umur (baton) ki sarparasti qubul ki to roze-qiyamat wo Allah azz-w-jall ke huzur is haal mein pesh hoga ke uska haath uski gardan ke sath bandha hoga, uski neki usey khol degi ya uska gunah usey halak kar dega. amaarat ka aaghaz malamat, uska wast baais nadaamat aur uska aakhir roze-qiyamat baais ruswai hoga.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3715,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Muawiya ! agar tumhen hukmrani mil jaey to Allah se darna aur adl karna.'' Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main hamesha us yaqin ke sath raha ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ki wajeh se kisi amal ke zariey aazmaya jaaunga yahan tak ke main aazmaish se dochaar ho gaya. rawahu Ahmed ."
3716,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sattar ki dahaai ke aaghaz se aur no umaron ki hukumat se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' ye chhe ahadis Imam Ahmed ne riwayat ki hain, aur Imam Behaqi ne hadees Muawiya '' dalaeelunnubuwah'' main naqal ki hai. rawahu Ahmed ."
3717,"Hazrat Yahya bin Haashim, Yunus bin abi Is-haq se aur wo apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jaisey tum hogey wesay tum par hukmran muqarrar kiye jaeyngey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
3718,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak badshah, zamin par Allah ka saya hai, jahan uska her mazloom banda panah hasil karta hai, jab wo adl karta hai to uskey liye ajr hai, aur ra'iyat ke zimma shukr karna hai, aur jab wo zulm karta hai to is par gunah hota hai aur ra'iyat ke zimma sabr karna hai.'' , ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3719,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak roze-qiyamat Allah ke bandon mein se maqam w martaba ke lihaz se sab se behtar shakhs adl karney wala naram mizaj hukmran hoga. jabkey roze-qiyamat Allah ke nazdik maqam w martaba ke lihaz se bad-tareen shakhs zalim aur sakht mizaj badshah hoga.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3720,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apney bhai ki taraf daraawni nazar se dekha to roze-qiyamat Allah usey daraaeyga.'' Imam Behaqi ne chaaron ahadis Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain, aur Yahya se marwi (bayan) hadees [ raqam 3717] ke barey mein farmaya : ye riwayat munqata hai aur iski riwayat zaeef hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3721,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah Taala farmata hai : main Allah hun, merey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, main baadshaahon ka Malik aur baadshaahon ka badshah hun, baadshaahon ke dil merey haath mein hain, aur jab bandey meri itaat kartey hain to main unke baadshaahon ke dil rehmat w shafqat ke sath un par pher deta hun, aur jab bandey meri nafarmani kartey hain to main unke dil narazi aur saza ke sath pher deta hun phir wo unhen burey azab se dochaar kartey hain, apney aap ko baadshaahon par baddua karney mein mashghool na rakho balke apney aap ko zikr aur Allah key saamney roney mein masroof rakho taake main tumhen tumharey hukmranon se mehfooz karun .'' isey abu-Nuem ne huliya mein bayan kya hai. (rawahu abu-Nuem fi huliya al-auliyaa ( ."
3722,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney kisi sahabi ko kisi kaam par lagatey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''(logon ko ajr w sawab ki) khushkhabri sanana, nafrat na dilana aur aasani paida karna tangi paida na karna.'' muttafaq aleh."
3723,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aasani paida karo, tangi paida na karo, sukoon pahunchao, nafrat na dilao.'' muttafaq aleh."
3724,"Hazrat abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke dada Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen ki taraf bhejtey huey farmaya : ''aasani paida karna, tangi paida na karna, khushkhabri sanana, nafrat na dilana, ittifaq rakhna aur ikhtilaf paida na karna.'' muttafaq aleh."
3725,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ehad shikni karney waley ke liye roze-qiyamat jhanda nasab kya jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : ye falan bin falan shakhs ki ehad shikni (ka nateeja) hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
3726,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat her ehad shikan ke liye eik jhanda hoga jiskey zariey wo pehchana jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh.
3727,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat her ehad shikan ki pusht par eik jhanda hoga.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''roze-qiyamat her ehad shikan ke liye eik jhanda hoga jo uski ehad shikni ke mutabiq buland kya jaeyga, sun lo! sarbarahe-mumlikat se badh kar kisi ehad shikan ki ehad shikni nahin.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3728,"Hazrat Amr bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah jis shakhs ko musalmanon ke kisi mamley ka sarparast bana dey aur wo unki zarurat , unki shikayat aur unki zaruraton ki pura karney mein rukawat bin jaey to Allah uski zarurat w shikayat aur uski hajat puri karney mein rukawat bin jata hai.'' Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ki zaruraton ka khayal rakhney ke liye eik aadmi ko muqarrar kya. Tirmizi aur Ahmed ki eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''Allah uski zarurat, hajat aur mohtaji ke waqt aasman ke darwazey band kar deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Ahmed ."
3729,"Hazrat Abu-Shamakh Azdi apney chacha zaad sey, jo ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi hain, riwayat kartey hain ke wo Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur unki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisey logon ke kisi mamley ki zimmedari sonpi jaey, phir wo musalmanon ya mazlumon ya hajat mandon ki zarooraton se darwazey band kar ley to Allah uski hajat aur zarurat ke waqt , jabkey wo intehai zaruratmand ho, apni rehmat ke darwazey band kar leta hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
3730,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab wo apney aamaal (hukmran) bhejtey to in par shart qaaim kartey ke tum turki ghodey par sawari na karogey aur na chhina hua aata ( میدہ ( khaaogey, na bareek ( umda ( libas pahnogey aur na logon ki zarooraton ko hal karney ki bajaey apney darwazey band karogey, agar tumne un mein se koi kaam bhi kya to tum saza ke mustahiq thehrogey, phir aap unhen al-wadaa karney ke liye unke sath chaltey. Imam Behaqi ne dono riwaayatein Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3731,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''haakim ghusse ki haalat mein do aadmiyon ke darmiyan faisla na karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3732,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab haakim faisla kartey waqt koshish karey aur durust faisla karey to uskey liye do ajr hain, aur jab faisla karey aur koshish ke bawajud ghalati ho jaey to uskey liye eik ajr hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3733,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko logon ka qazi bana diya gaya goya wo chhuri ke baghair zibeh kar diya gaya .'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3734,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qaza ka khaahishmand ho aur wo mutalba karey to usey uski zaat ke supurd kar diya jata hai, aur jisey is par majbur kar diya jaey to Allah is par eik farishta nazil farma deta hai jo usko durust rakhta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3735,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qazi teen qism ke hain, un mein se eik jannati aur do jahannami hain, wo qazi jannati hai jisney haq pehchan kar uskey mutabiq faisla kya, aur wo qazi jisney haq pehchan kar faisla mein zulm kya to wo jahannami hai, aur wo aadmi jisney jihalat ki bina par logon ke darmiyan faisla kya to wo bhi jahannami hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3736,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne musalmanon ki qaza talab ki aur wo usey muyassar aa gaee, phir uska adl uskey zulm par ghalib raha to uskey liye jannat hai, aur jis shakhs ke adl par uska zulm ghalib raha to uskey liye jahannam hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3737,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab unhen Yamen bheja to farmaya : ''jab koi muqadma tumharey samney pesh aaeyga to tum kaisey faisla karogey?'' unhoney arz kya : main Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla karunga . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum Allah ki kitab mein na paao?'' arz kya : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ke mutabiq, farmaya : ''agar tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat mein na paao?'' arz kya : main apni raey se ijtihaad karunga, aur koi kasar nahin utha rakhunga, wo bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( az-raahe-musarrat) merey seeney par haath maar kar farmaya : ''her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qaasid ko is chiz ki tofiq ata farmaai jisey Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pasand farmatey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi."
3738,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Yamen ka qazi bana kar bheja to maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey bhej rahey hain, jabkey main nau-umr hun aur mujhey qaza ke barey mein ilm bhi nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak an-qareeb Allah terey dil ki raahnumai kerega aur teri zaban ko istiaqamat ata farmaeyga , jab do aadmi terey paas muqadma lekar ayen to doosrey fariq ki baat suney baghair pehley fariq ke haq mein faisla na karna kyonkey ye laaiq tar hai ke terey liye qaza wazeh ho jaey.'' Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, uskey baad mujhey faisley karney mein shak nahin hua . aur Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''main tumharey darmiyan apni raey se faisla karunga .'' ko ham ( '' baab الاقضیۃ w الشھادات '' ( mein insha Allah Taala zikr karengey. ( rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ( ."
3739,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo haakim bhi logon ke darmiyan faisley karta hai wo qiyamat ke din is haal mein aaeyga ke eik farishta usey guddi se pakdey hoga, phir wo apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaeyga agar Allah Taala ne kaha : usey phenk do, wo usey chaalis saal (ki masafat ki gehraai) ke gadhey mein phenk dega.'' ( rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3740,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat aadil qazi bhi ye aarzu kerega ke kaash! usney do aadmiyon ke darmiyan kabhi eik khajoor ka bhi faisla na kya hota .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3741,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak qazi zulm na karey to Allah uskey sath hota hai, jab wo zulm karta hai to wo us se alag ho jata hai aur shetan uskey sath lag jata hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''jab wo zulm karta hai to Allah usey uskey nafs ke supurd kar deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3742,"Hazrat Saeed bin musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik musalman aur eik Yahudi umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas muqadma lekar aaye to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mehsus kya ke Yahudi haq par hai isliye unhoney Yahudi ke haq mein faisla kar diya to Yahudi ne unhen kaha : Allah ki qasam! aapney haq ke mutabiq faisla kya, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey durra maara aur farmaya : tujhey kaisey pata chala? Yahudi ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! ham Torah mein) likha hua ( paatey hain ke jo qazi haq ke mutabiq faisla karta hai to uskey daain baain eik eik farishta hota hai, wo dono usey haq ke liye durust rakhtey hain, aur usey haq deney ki koshish kartey hain, jab wo haq chhod deta hai to wo dono (aasman ki taraf) ooper chadh jatey hain, aur usey chhod detey hain.'' rawahu Malik."
3743,"Hazrat ibne-Mohab se riwayat hai ke Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''logon ke darmiyan qazi banna qubul karo . unhoney kaha : ameerul-momeneen! aap mujhey maaf nahin farma detey ? unhoney farmaya : aap usey napasand kyon kartey hain, jabkey aap ke walid faisley kya kartey they. unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs qazi ho aur wo insaf se faisley karey to ye ziyada laaiq hai ke wo ( qazi ( se barabar barabar reh jaey.'' Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey baad unhen nahin kaha . rawahu Tirmizi ."
3744,"Rizeen ki Naafe ki sanad se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ameerul-momeneen! main do aadmiyon ke darmiyan bhi faisla nahin karunga, unhoney farmaya : aap ke walid to faisla kya kartey they. unhoney kaha : merey walid ko kisi masle mein ishkal hota to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochh liya kartey they, agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kisi masle mein uljhan hoti to wo Jibrael se poochh letey they, jabkey main aisa koi shakhs nahin paata jis se main poochh lun aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisney Allah ki panah hasil ki to usney eik azeem zaat ki panah hasil ki.'' aur maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs Allah ke wastey se panah talab kar ley to usey panah de-do.'' aur main Allah ki panah chahta hun ke tum mujhey qazi banaao. unhoney us se darguzar kya aur farmaya : kisi ko na batana. rawahu rizeen ."
3745,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main na tumhen deta hun aur na tum se rokta hun, main to taqseem karney wala hun main to usi jagah par kharch karta hun jahan ke mutalliq mujhey hukm diya jata hai.'' Bukhari ."
3746,"Hazrat Khaula ansaariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kuch log Allah ke maal ( baitulmal ( mein nahaq tasarruf kartey hain, roze-qiyamat unke liye ( jahannam ki) aag hai.'' Bukhari ."
3747,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa baney to unhoney farmaya : ''meri qom jaanti hai ke mera karobar merey ehle khana ke ikhrajat ke liye kafi tha, mujhey musalmanon ke maamlat ke hawaley se mashghool kar diya gaya hai lihaza aale-abu-Bakar us maal se khaeyngey aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) musalmanon ke liye kaam karengey. Bukhari."
3748,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham jis shakhs ko kisi kaam par muqarrar karen aur usey tankhwaah bhi den, aur phir uskey ilawa jo maal wo hasil kerega wo khayanat hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3749,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein (amaarat ka ( kaam kya to aapney mujhey ujrat ata farmaai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3750,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Yamen ki taraf bheja , jab main chala to aapney merey peechey qaasid bhej kar mujhey wapis bula liya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya to janta hai ke maine tumhari taraf (qaasid) kyon bheja? (us liye ke tumhen koi wasiyat karun ( tum meri ijazat ke baghair koi chiz na lena, kyonkey (agar tum logey to ( wo khayanat hogi , aur jo shakhs khayanat kerega wo us khayanat ko roze-qiyamat lekar hazir hoga. maine isi liye tumhen wapis bulaya tha, ab tum apney kaam ke liye jaao.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3751,"Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs hamara aamil (hukmran, governer (ho (aur agar uski biwi na ho to wo baitulmal mein se haq mehar ada karkey) shaadi kar ley. agar uska khaadim na ho to wo khaadim kharid ley aur agar uski rihaaish na ho to wo rihaaish kharid ley.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jisney uskey ilawa kuch hasil kya to wo khayanat karney wala hai.''"
3752,"Hazrat Adi bin Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logo ! tum mein se jis shakhs ko hamarey kisi kaam par aamil muqarrar kya jaey aur wo is mein se soi ya us se koi chhoti badi chiz ham se chupa ley to wo khayanat karney wala hai, wo roze-qiyamat usey lekar aaeyga.'' (ye baat sun kar) ansaar mein se eik aadmi khada hua aur usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! aap apni tafweez karda zimmedari mujh se wapis ley lin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo kis liye?'' usney arz kya : maine aap ko aisey aisey farmatey huey suna hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ye kehta hun, ham jis shakhs ko aamil muqarrar karen to usey chahiye ke wo hasil honey wali her qaleel w Kasir chiz pesh karey. aur phir is mein se jo usey diya jaey wo usey le-ley aur jis chiz se usey rok diya jaey to wo us se ruk jaey.'' Muslim, Abu-Dawood. aur alfaz hadees Abu-Dawood ke hain. rawahu Muslim w Abu-Dawood ."
3753,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rishwat deney waley aur rishwat leney waley par lanat farmaai hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
3754,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi ne Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
3755,Hazrat Imam Ahmed ne usey riwayat kya hai aur Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein usey Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. aur is mein ye izafa naqal kya hai : ( وَالرَّائِشَ ( yani jo dono (rishwat deney waley aur rishwat leney waley) ke darmiyan maamla tey karata hai (us par bhi lanat farmaai). (rawahu Ahmed w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
3756,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey pegham bheja ke main apna aslaha aur kapdey jama karkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kar dun, wo bayan kartey hain, main hazire-khidmat hua to aap wuzu farma rahey they, aapney farmaya : ''Amr! maine tumhari taraf pegham bheja tha ke main tumhen kisi muhim par rawana karun, Allah tumhen salaamat rakhey, tumhen maale-ghanimat ata farmaai aur main tumhen kuch maal ata karunga.'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! meri hijrat maal ki khatir nahin thi, wo to mehaz Allah aur uskey Rasool ki khatir thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' halal maal, Saleh mard ke liye achcha hai.'' Sharahus-sunnah aur Imam Ahmed ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai, uskey alfaz ye hain : ''saleh insan ke liye halal maal behtar hai.'' (fi Sharahus-sunnah w Ahmed ( ."
3757,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi ki sifarish ki, aur wo usey ( sifarish karney ( ki wajeh se koi tohfa pesh karey aur sifarish karney wala us tohfe ko qubul karey to wo sood ke darwazon mein se eik badey darwazey mein dakhil ho gaya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3758,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar logon ko mehaz unke dawe ki buniyad par dey diya jaey to log aadmiyon ke khoon aur amwaal ka dawa karney lagengey, lekin qism mudda-aleh ke zimmey hai.'' Imam nauwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne sahih Muslim ki Shareh mein farmaya : Behaqi ki riwayat mein Hasan ya sahih sanad ke sath ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) marfoo riwayat mein ye alfaz ziyada hain : ''lekin muddai ke zimmey daleel w gawahi pesh karna hai aur jo shakhs inkar karey uskey zimmey qism hai.'' rawahu Muslim w Shareh Nawwi w sunan al-kubra Behqi."
3759,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi musalman ka maal hasil karney ke liye qasdan jhooti qism uthaey to wo roze-qiyamat jab Allah se mulaqat karega to wo us shakhs par naraz hoga.'' Allah Taala ne uski tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil farmaaey : ''be-shak jo log Allah ke ehad aur apni qasmon ke badley mein thodi si qeemat wasul kartey hain. . . . . . . . .'' muttafaq aleh."
3760,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apni qism ke zariey kisi musalman shakhs ka haq hasil kiya to Allah ne uskey liye jahannam ko wajib kar diya aur is par jannat ko haram qarar dey diya.'' (ye baat sun kar) kisi aadmi ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! chahey (chaahe) wo maamuli si chiz ho? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khuwah wo peelu ki shaakh ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
3761,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main bhi eik insan hun, tum apney muqaddamaat merey paas latey ho. aur mumkin hai ke tum mein se koi apni daleel doosrey ki nisbat ziyada fasaahat ke sath pesh kar ley aur main jo us se sunoon uskey haq mein faisla kar dun, jis shakhs ko uskey (musalman) bhai ke haq mein se koi chiz de-di jaey to wo usey hasil na karey, (goya is tarah) main usey (jahannam ki) aag ka eik tukda dey raha hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
3762,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sakht jhagdalu shakhs Allah ke nazdik intehai naa-pasandida shakhs hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3763,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qism aur eik gawah ke sath faisla kiya. rawahu Muslim.
3764,"Hazrat Alqama bin Waael apney walid se riwayat kartey hain eik aadmi Hazare-maut se aur eik aadmi kanda se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to hizrami ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! us shakhs ne meri zamin par qabza kar liya hai, Kandi ne arz kiya : ye zamin meri hai aur merey qabze mein hai, uska is par koi haq nahin, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hizrami se farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas koi daleel hai? '' usney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum us se qism ley lo.'' usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo to eik faajir (badkar) shakhs hai, wo qism ki koi parwah nahin karta hai aur na kisi chiz se perhez karta hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen us se yehi kuchh mil sakta hai.'' jab wo (Kandi) qism khaney chala to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar usney uska nahaq maal khaney ke liye qism uthai to ye Allah se us haal mein mulaqat kerega ke wo us se aeraz farmaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
3765,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisney kisi aisi chiz ka dawa kiya jo ke uski nahin to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' rawahu Muslim.
3766,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen behtareen gawah ke mutalliq na bataaun? ye wo hai jo us (gawahi) ke talab kiye janey se pehley apni gawahi pesh kar dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3767,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey daur ke log (Sahaba kiraam) sab se behtar hain, phir wo log jo unke sath hain (taabea'in). aur phir wo jo unke sath hain, phir kuchh aisey log aaeyngey ke un mein se kisi ki gawahi uski qism par aur uski qism uski gawahi par sabqat ley jaeygi.'' muttafaq aleh."
3768,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik qom par qism pesh ki to unhoney (qasam uthaney mein) jaldi ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm farmaya ke qism ke barey mein unke darmiyan qura andazi ki jaey ke un mein se kon half uthaeyga. Bukhari.
3769,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gawah pesh karna muddai ke zimme hai aur qism uske zimme hai jis par ilzam hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi.
3770,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) do aadmiyon ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, jinhonne meeras ke mutalliq aap ki khidmat mein muqadma pesh kiya, un dono ke paas koi daleel aur gawahi nahin thi. un dono ka mehaz dawa hi tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main jis shakhs ko uskey (musalman) bhai ke haq mein se kuchh de-dun to (haqeeqat mein) main usey (jahannam ki) aag ka eik tukda kaat kar dey raha hun.'' (ye sun kar) dono mein her eik arz karney laga, Allah ke Rasool ! mera ye haq merey sathi ka hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(aisey) nahin, tum dono jaao aur insaf ke taqaazey purey kartey huey taqseem kar lo, phir dono qura andazi karo phir tum dono mein se her eik apna hissey apney sathi ke liye halal qarar dey.'' dusri riwayat mein hai farmaya : ''is chiz ke barey mein mujh par koi chiz nazil nahin hui isliye main tumharey darmiyan apni raey se faisla karta hun.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3771,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ne eik chopaey par dawa kiya, aur un mein se her eik ne gawah pesh kiya ke usney apney chopaey ko jufti karaya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq us shakhs ke haq mein faisla farmaya jiskey wo (qabze) mein tha. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3772,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik oont ke mutalliq daawa kiya to un mein se her eik ne do gawah pesh kiye, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey un dono ke darmiyan nisf-nisf (aadha-aadha) taqseem farma diya. Nasai aur ibne-Maja mein unhin se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai ke do aadmiyon ne eik oont ke mutalliq daawa kiya aur un mein se kisi ke paas bhi gawah nahin they, lihaza Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey un dono ke darmiyan taqseem farma diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
3773,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ne kisi janwer ke barey mein jhagda kiya aur un dono ke paas koi gawahi nahin thi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam par qura andazi karo.'' (jis ka qura nikal aaye wo qism dey) rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3774,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi se qism leney ka irada kiya to farmaya : ''Allah ki qism uthaao jiskey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin ke tumharey paas us shakhs (yani muddai) ki koi chiz nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3775,"Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, meri aur eik Yahudi ki kuchh mushtarka zamin thi, usney merey hissey ka inkar kar diya main apna muqadma lekar usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas koi gawahi hai? ''maine arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Yahudi se farmaya : ''qasam uthaao.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! wo to qism utha lega aur meri zamin ghasab kar lega. tab Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''be-shak jo log Allah ke ehad aur apni qasmon ke badle mein thodi si qeemat hasil kartey hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3776,"Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Kandi aur hizrami shakhs ne Yamen ki zamin ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein muqadma pesh kiya to hizrami ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! is shakhs ke walid ne meri zamin ghasab kar li thi aur wo ab iskey qabze mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas gawah hai?'' usney arz kiya, nahin, lekin main us se qism lunga (is tarah ke) Allah ki qism ! wo nahin janta ke be-shak meri zamin ko uskey walid ne ghasab kiya hai, Kandi qism ke liye tayyar hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qism ke zariey maal hasil karta hai to wo Allah se us haal mein mulaqat kerega ke wo shakhs ''ajzam'' hoga.'' (yani uska haath kataa hua hoga ya uskey paas koi daleel nahin hogi.) chunanche us Kandi ne arz kiya : wo zamin uski hi hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3777,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Unnais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke sath shirk karna , waliden ki nafarmani karna aur jhooti qism khana kabeera gunahon mein se hai. aur jis shakhs ne Allah ki pukhta qism uthai aur is mein machar ke par ke barabar (jhoot) dakhil kar diya to roze-qiyamat tak uskey dil main eik nukta laga diya jata hai.'' Tirmizi. aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3778,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs merey is member ke paas jhooti qism uthata hai chahey (chaahe) wo sabz (hara) miswak ke mutalliq ho to uska thikana jahannam mein bana diya jata hai ya uskey liye jahannam wajib ho jati hai.'' rawahu Malik, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3779,"Hazrat Khuraim bin Fatiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Fajr ada ki, jab aap farigh huey to khadey ho kar teen martaba farmaya : ''jhooti gawahi ko Allah ke sath shirk karney ke barabar qarar diya gaya hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''paleedi yani buton ki puja se bacho aur jhooti baat (jhooti gawahi) se bacho, Allah ke sath shirk na kartey huey uski taraf yak-su ho jaao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3780,Hazrat Imam Ahmed aur Imam Tirmizi ne Aiman bin Khuraim se riwayat kiya hai albatta ibne-Maja ne qirat ka zikr nahin kiya. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi.
3781,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khayanat karney waley mard ki gawahi jayez nahin aur na khayanat karney wali aurat ki, jis shakhs par had qaaim ki gaee ho uski gawahi bhi manzoor nahin aur na dushmani rakhney waley shakhs ki apney bhai ke khilaf, aur wala (azaadi) ke barey mein muttahim (jis par jhoot wagaira ka ilzaam laga ho) shakhs ki gawahi jayez nahin aur na qurbat ke barey mein muttahim shakhs ki aur na hi ehale bait (yani khandan) ke barey mein aisey shakhs ki gawahi jayez hai jis ka kharcha uskey khandan ke zimme ho.'' Tirmizi. aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye hadees gharib hai aur Yazid bin Ziyad dimashqi raawi munkirul-hadees hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3782,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khayanat karney waley mard ki shahadat (gawahi) jayez nahin aur na khayanat karney wali aurat ki, na zaani mard ki gawahi jayez hai aur na zaaniya aurat ki aur dushmani rakhney waley shakhs ki apney bhai ke mutalliq gawahi jayez nahin, aur khandan ke zere-kifalat shakhs ki us khandan ke mutalliq gawahi qubul nahin ki jaeygi.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3783,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ganwaar ki basti mein rihaaish pazeer (rahne wale) shakhs ke khilaf gawahi jayez nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3784,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do aadmiyon ke darmiyan faisla farmaya to aapney jis shakhs ke khilaf faisla farmaya jab wo wapis janey laga to usney kaha : ''merey liye Allah kafi hai aur wo achchha karsaz hai.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah Taala beja narmi aur nadani par malamat farmata hai, balke tumhen ehtiyat karni chahiye, jab koshish ke bawajud koi khilafe-tawaqqo waqia ghalib aa jaey to tum kaho : ''merey liye Allah kafi hai aur wo achchha karsaz hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3785,"Hazrat Bahaz-bin Haakim apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko tohmat par qaid mein rakha. Imam Tirmizi aur Imam Nasai ne ye izafa naqal kiya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey chhod diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi aur Nasai."
3786,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke dono fariq haakim ke samney bithaaey jaeyngey. rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
